      "role": "user",
      "content": "pretending doesn't really work though. it's just exhausting to keep acting like i'm okay when i'm actually drowning. the weight of it all just makes me feel like there's no point in trying to fix things or move forward. i just want to find a way to finally be at peace, like a way to just... not have to deal with any of this ever again. is that even possible? to just escape it all for real?",
